channel.title: I need some help
channel.description:
Yes, i know i will probably sound like an ultra-noob when asking this.
Has anyone found the TabID field yet? I've been looking around for it, but i can't seem to locate it. My first thought was to check the keypress event (since they added tab switching with the F-keys), and i found it in Class60. I've tried to debug it from there, but i still can't find it. I would appreciate any help i could get regarding this problem.
Thank You.
